Hi everyone
I'm Anshul, from Gurgaon, India. I'm a brand strategist & designer, recently started my branding & marketing studio <http://www.bettr.studio|Bettr Studio>. We help natural product brands to increase customer engagement, retention & revenue using branding, web-dev & content. It's a small team of 3 - me, a developer & a writer.

I'm very new in this space so I'm hoping to learn more about content marketing & how to use it to grow my personal as well as business brand.

Excited to learn from you all. :slightly_smiling_face:

text: Hi everyone! I'm <https://www.caitlandconley.com/|Caitland> (she/her) living in Brooklyn by way of North Florida. I started my career in digital marketing in the travel/hospitality sphere and have since lived _many_ lives as a freelance copywriter (industries like beauty, SaaS, and food + beverage), fledgling SEO, and even a part-time baker. Today I work as an SEO content strategist for Vimeo. I was drawn to Superpath as a way to build community and find mentorship in our increasingly digital content world. I imagine I'll occasionally look for freelancers from certain channels in this group, but more, I'm excited to learn from you talented folks! :sunny:
